short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy, Copy all Tabs URLs to the clipboard. Paste, Open Tabs all the URLs in the clipboard.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can copy the URLs of all open tabs to the clipboard or open all URLs in the clipboard at once.

 - Copy, Copy the URLs of all open tabs to the clipboard in any format (text, json, custom).
 - Paste, Open all URLs in the clipboard at once. The URLs to be opened can be filtered.
